videos.title: Beastie Break Out  Standard
videos.description:
The banning of the red Leyline could potentially open up the metagame on different styles of aggro. Maybe Patchwork Bestie and Break Out can be your new favorite aggro deck!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
